### Test Reporting API Examples

### 1. Weekly Report
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports/weekly
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2026-03-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-07"
}

### 2. Custom Payroll Report (Monthly)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports/custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromDate": "2026-03-01",
  "toDate": "2026-03-31",
  "reportType": "payroll"
}

### 3. Custom Attendance Report (Monthly)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports/custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromDate": "2026-03-01",
  "toDate": "2026-03-31",
  "reportType": "attendance"
}

### 4. Custom Loans Report (Quarterly)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports/custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromDate": "2026-01-01",
  "toDate": "2026-03-31",
  "reportType": "loans"
}

### 5. Custom Department Report (Yearly)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports/custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromDate": "2026-01-01",
  "toDate": "2026-12-31",
  "reportType": "department"
}

### 6. Export Report to CSV
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports/export
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportTitle": "Weekly Report",
  "generatedDate": "2026-03-01",
  "periodStart": "2026-03-01",
  "periodEnd": "2026-03-07",
  "summary": {
    "totalEmployees": 25,
    "totalAttendanceRecords": 125,
    "totalLateMinutes": 180,
    "totalOvertimeMinutes": 240
  },
  "details": [
    {
      "employeeName": "Ahmed Mohamed",
      "attendances": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "employeeName": "Ahmed Mohamed",
          "date": "2026-03-01",
          "actualStart": "09:15",
          "actualEnd": "18:30",
          "lateMinutes": 15,
          "overtimeMinutes": 90
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### 7. Error Case - Invalid Report Type
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports/custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromDate": "2026-03-01",
  "toDate": "2026-03-31",
  "reportType": "invalid_type"
}
